items.name: happycapy
items.tagline: The agent-native computer, for the rest of us
items.description: OpenClaw alternative, in your browser. And now on your phone. No setup. No learning curve. No security risks. Just open it and go. Happycapy turns browser into an agent-native computer powered by Claude Code. With a GUI friendly for everyday user, it lets anyone get real work done in one single place from coding and design to everyday tasks. This is computing for everyone. For creators. For builders. For people who just want things done. For productivity. And for fun.

items.name: Revo AI Email Assistant
items.tagline: AI with accurate replies that tackle the next-step tasks
items.description: Revo for Email is an intelligent inbox layer that connects your meetings, Slack, and CRM to answer emails for you. Built for Gmail, Outlook and is ready in seconds. No more searching. No more typing. No more guessing.

items.name: Atyla
items.tagline: The SEO tool for ChatGPT, Gemini and AI search engines
items.description: Atyla helps marketing teams track and improve brand visibility on AI search engines like ChatGPT, Perplexity, Gemini and Claude. As AI replaces traditional search, Atyla shows how often your brand is mentioned in AI answers, which competitors are recommended instead, and how to improve your presence. Built for GEO (Generative Engine Optimization), Atyla turns AI visibility into a measurable growth channel.

items.name: Doraverse's All-in-One AI for Meetings
items.tagline: Meet in any language with live translations
items.description: To better support daily work, we‚Äôve added new meeting features to Doraverse‚Äôs all-in-one AI platform, removing friction and eliminating follow-up work. It runs meetings end to end with live translation in 60+ languages, automatic transcripts, notes, action items, and AI assistant you can ask on the spot. Bot or no bot. Enterprise-grade security by default.

items.name: Oz by Warp
items.tagline: Run hundreds of cloud agents in parallel
items.description: Oz is an orchestration platform for cloud agents. Launch hundreds of cloud agents in minutes, from Warp, CLI or even your phone. Wake up to production-ready PRs.

items.name: Willow for Developers
items.tagline: Dictation for Cursor & AI IDEs, the fastest way to vibe code
items.description: With this release, Willow has improved the voice dictation experience for developers. You can speak directly to AI IDEs like Cursor, Antigravity, and more with dictation that is 3x more accurate than built-in options. New developer features include: file tagging for richer context, built-in recognition of technical terms and acronyms (SQL, API, REST, etc.), and faster dictation into prompt editors. Works across Mac and Windows devices.

items.name: JumprAI
items.tagline: Find any moment inside YouTube videos with AI search
items.description: JumprAI lets you search inside YouTube videos using AI. Instead of scrubbing through timelines, just describe what you want (‚Äúfunniest moment,‚Äù ‚Äúsetup tutorial‚Äù) and jump straight there. It uses semantic search to understand meaning, not just keywords. Works automatically on videos with captions, integrates smoothly into YouTube, and keeps your data private. And it's totally FREE :) Enjoy !
